<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="22500000t" end="40800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">我说十条寺</p>
<p begin="40800000t" end="64200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">这种道地的鳗鱼专卖店</p>
<p begin="64200000t" end="87500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">你有一个人来过吗</p>
<p begin="87500000t" end="110900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">不, 我没一个人来过</p>
<p begin="118400000t" end="140100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">鳗鱼虽然好吃, 但价格不怎么亲民</p>
<p begin="140100000t" end="168000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">要是能毫无顾虑地来这种店用餐</p>
<p begin="168000000t" end="188000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">果然还是有一定的年纪</p>
<p begin="188000000t" end="206400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">或相当程度的经历吧</p>
<p begin="206400000t" end="226800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">我想也是</p>
<p begin="226800000t" end="246400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">那么那个人是怎么回事呢</p>
<p begin="253500000t" end="267700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">天晓得</p>
<p begin="309000000t" end="327800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">请给我一份特上鳗鱼饭</p>
<p begin="536700000t" end="560100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="560100000t" end="588500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="588500000t" end="611000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="611000000t" end="639300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="639300000t" end="661900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="661900000t" end="690200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="690200000t" end="712700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="712700000t" end="741100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="741100000t" end="793200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="793200000t" end="827400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="827400000t" end="867100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="882500000t" end="926700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="926700000t" end="980500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="980500000t" end="1028900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="1028900000t" end="1057700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="1057700000t" end="1091900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="1232800000t" end="1252900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">你觉得她看起来像几岁</p>
<p begin="1252900000t" end="1286600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">高中…不, 应该是国中生吧</p>
<p begin="1286600000t" end="1314600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">气质和举止倒是挺早熟的</p>
<p begin="1314600000t" end="1354200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">是哪家的深闺千金吗</p>
<p begin="1421400000t" end="1441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">梶尾, 别盯着人家看</p>
<p begin="1441000000t" end="1452700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">真是个谜啊</p>
<p begin="1452700000t" end="1465200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">独自来到鳗鱼专卖店</p>
<p begin="1465200000t" end="1498100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">还点了特上鳗鱼饭的奇异少女</p>
<p begin="1498100000t" end="1510200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">好像洋娃娃喔</p>
<p begin="1510200000t" end="1528600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">真怀疑她有没有内脏</p>
<p begin="1528600000t" end="1551500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">没有内脏怎么吃鳗鱼</p>
<p begin="1551500000t" end="1581500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">可能是专吃鳗鱼饭的机关人偶啊</p>
<p begin="1581500000t" end="1602400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">什么不吃偏偏吃鳗鱼饭吗</p>
<p begin="1602400000t" end="1632000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">你也想太多了吧, 就这么在意吗</p>
<p begin="1632000000t" end="1649900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">谜团还是不要有比较好</p>
<p begin="1649900000t" end="1690000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">为了能够好好吃饭, 晚上好好睡觉</p>
<p begin="1697900000t" end="1731300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">今天我实在不想把这种事挂在心上</p>
<p begin="1743400000t" end="1772500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">先别管那女孩出现在这里的理由了</p>
<p begin="1772500000t" end="1815900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">你为什么突然邀我大白天来吃鳗鱼饭?</p>
<p begin="1815900000t" end="1838000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">而且还是到这么高级的店</p>
<p begin="1853100000t" end="1881800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我太太雪枝已经过世半年了</p>
<p begin="1891400000t" end="1905200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">自从雪枝过世后</p>
<p begin="1905200000t" end="1924000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">我一直觉得身体很沉</p>
<p begin="1924000000t" end="1946100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">每天晚上都睡不好</p>
<p begin="1946100000t" end="1985700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我有去医院检查, 但完全查不出问题</p>
<p begin="1985700000t" end="2024900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">结果只能说是出于心理引发的身体不适</p>
<p begin="2024900000t" end="2064900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">心灵这种东西还真是无法控制呢</p>
<p begin="2080400000t" end="2108300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">不过我感觉终于好转了</p>
<p begin="2108300000t" end="2146300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">这几天睡得比较好, 体重也开始恢复</p>
<p begin="2146300000t" end="2173400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我想说差不多该重振旗鼓了</p>
<p begin="2173400000t" end="2214200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">所以决定来吃鳗鱼饭给自己打打气</p>
<p begin="2214200000t" end="2228000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">这样啊</p>
<p begin="2228000000t" end="2262600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">毕竟太太过世似乎让你很不好受</p>
<p begin="2268000000t" end="2294700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">那么选择吃鳗鱼饭是正确的选择</p>
<p begin="2294700000t" end="2323100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">鳗鱼自奈良时代以来就被认为对身体很好</p>
<p begin="2327700000t" end="2355600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">万叶集也提过吃鳗鱼能舒缓中暑症状</p>
<p begin="2367700000t" end="2410300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">你从以前就知道很多不重要的小知识呢</p>
<p begin="2410300000t" end="2444900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">再加点个烤鳗肝, 鳗鱼卷和炸鳗鱼骨吧</p>
<p begin="2444900000t" end="2462000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">老板娘, 我们要加点</p>
<p begin="2462000000t" end="2475800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">马上来</p>
<p begin="2481600000t" end="2495800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">换个角度思考吧</p>
<p begin="2506600000t" end="2528700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">那女孩会来这家店的理由</p>
<p begin="2528700000t" end="2558300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我们很难从有限的情报推测</p>
<p begin="2558300000t" end="2571700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">就是说啊</p>
<p begin="2571700000t" end="2588390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">但我们可以反过来思考</p>
<p begin="2593800000t" end="2632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">为什么我们会遭遇如此奇异的现象</p>
<p begin="2632600000t" end="2671000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">人们自古以来就把稀奇或不可思议的现象</p>
<p begin="2671000000t" end="2705100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">解释为吉兆或凶兆</p>
<p begin="2705100000t" end="2741800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">这对我们来说会不会也是某种征兆呢</p>
<p begin="2741800000t" end="2752300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">征兆?</p>
<p begin="2752300000t" end="2800700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">古人有言, 黑猫经过面前会发生坏事</p>
<p begin="2800700000t" end="2825700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">或是看到茶梗立起来会发生好事对吧</p>
<p begin="2834400000t" end="2867000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">也有遇上灵车很不吉利的说法呢</p>
<p begin="2867000000t" end="2893200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">那在道地鳗鱼专卖店</p>
<p begin="2893200000t" end="2924100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">遇见独自享用鳗鱼饭的少女会表示什么呢</p>
<p begin="2931200000t" end="2974200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">我也希望这么楚楚可怜的少女能当作吉兆</p>
<p begin="2981700000t" end="3001300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">不过既然是在鳗鱼专卖店</p>
<p begin="3001300000t" end="3032100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">出现的又是看不出是不是人类</p>
<p begin="3032100000t" end="3055500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">外貌华美吸睛的人物</p>
<p begin="3055500000t" end="3080900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">那么应该带有某种意义或象征才对</p>
<p begin="3095100000t" end="3114700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">鳗鱼被视为神佛…</p>
<p begin="3114700000t" end="3146800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">尤其是虚空藏菩萨的使者</p>
<p begin="3153900000t" end="3190600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">虚空藏菩萨司掌福德和智慧</p>
<p begin="3190600000t" end="3222300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">左手持有象征福德的如意宝珠</p>
<p begin="3222300000t" end="3251900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">右手则握着代表智慧的宝剑</p>
<p begin="3251900000t" end="3268600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">智慧啊</p>
<p begin="3268600000t" end="3309500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">此外鳗鱼在关东和关西的切法也有所不同</p>
<p begin="3314100000t" end="3333700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">我记得关东是从背部</p>
<p begin="3333700000t" end="3353300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">关西则是从腹部切开对吧</p>
<p begin="3358300000t" end="3372500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">说是因为关东有较多武士</p>
<p begin="3372500000t" end="3398800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">所以忌讳令人联想到切腹的下刀方式</p>
<p begin="3398800000t" end="3418800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">民间是有那种解释</p>
<p begin="3418800000t" end="3455900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">不过较为广泛的说法是</p>
<p begin="3460900000t" end="3475900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">这家店的鳗鱼…</p>
<p begin="3491300000t" end="3513500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">似乎是使用关西的调理法</p>
<p begin="3523100000t" end="3557300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">也就是暗示着"切腹"的鱼腹切法</p>
<p begin="3557300000t" end="3586400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">而鳗鱼也因其表面布满粘液难以捕捉</p>
<p begin="3586400000t" end="3611900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">被用来比喻"巧妙地逃脱"</p>
<p begin="3620200000t" end="3637300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">将这些要素综合起来</p>
<p begin="3637300000t" end="3669900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">那个脱俗的女孩就象征着虚空藏菩萨</p>
<p begin="3669900000t" end="3711600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">鳗鱼则代表企图巧妙脱罪的罪人</p>
<p begin="3711600000t" end="3735800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">所以这是在暗示虚空藏菩萨</p>
<p begin="3735800000t" end="3768700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">会以智慧宝剑逮住意图摆脱罪嫌的罪人</p>
<p begin="3768700000t" end="3792100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">并将其逼入切腹的下场</p>
<p begin="3792100000t" end="3814200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">竟然全都衔接起来了呢</p>
<p begin="3814200000t" end="3824600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">是啊</p>
<p begin="3824600000t" end="3839200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">那女孩的出现</p>
<p begin="3839200000t" end="3854600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">或许代表着有智慧的人</p>
<p begin="3854600000t" end="3892600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">将会揭露并制裁罪恶的天启呢</p>
<p begin="3900500000t" end="3935100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">梶尾, 是你把你太太…</p>
<p begin="3951400000t" end="3966800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">把雪枝杀死的对吧</p>
<p begin="4008500000t" end="4026500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">我想到一个问题</p>
<p begin="4026500000t" end="4075700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">虚空藏菩萨把自己的使者吃掉没关系吗</p>
<p begin="4075700000t" end="4089900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">身为菩萨</p>
<p begin="4089900000t" end="4121600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">要怎么对待自己的使者应该是祂的自由吧</p>
<p begin="4129500000t" end="4164500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">好了, 你为什么认为是我杀死雪枝的</p>
<p begin="4164500000t" end="4207900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">她在半年前走夜路遭到抢劫</p>
<p begin="4207900000t" end="4235800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">强盗抢走包包时她被推了一把而跌倒</p>
<p begin="4235800000t" end="4275500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">结果撞破了头, 不幸身亡</p>
<p begin="4275500000t" end="4314300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">那只是警方从发现遗体的状况所下的判断</p>
<p begin="4314300000t" end="4352600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">实际上根本没人目击她被强盗袭击的瞬间</p>
<p begin="4363100000t" end="4391400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">如果你推她去撞墙把她杀死之后</p>
<p begin="4391400000t" end="4413500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">再伪装成强盗袭击</p>
<p begin="4413500000t" end="4428500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">也能制造一样的现场</p>
<p begin="4441900000t" end="4460200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">虽然没出人命</p>
<p begin="4460200000t" end="4477700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">但在雪枝被袭击之前</p>
<p begin="4477700000t" end="4506500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">就已经有好几起手法相同的抢案了</p>
<p begin="4506500000t" end="4534100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">雪枝过世后也发生了好几起</p>
<p begin="4534100000t" end="4569500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">所以警方才会以强盗杀人的方向搜查</p>
<p begin="4569500000t" end="4623300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">假设你是刻意模仿强盗犯案的话就说得通</p>
<p begin="4623300000t" end="4651300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">又或者一连串的抢案本身</p>
