<p begin="9313800000t" end="9350100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">- 梶尾! 你这家伙!</p>
<p begin="9356000000t" end="9370100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">本来今天去自首</p>
<p begin="9370100000t" end="9395200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">就能为这一切画下句点的</p>
<p begin="9395200000t" end="9427700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">为什么这女孩会知道真相</p>
<p begin="9443600000t" end="9454000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">这样啊</p>
<p begin="9454000000t" end="9467700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">这样就能解释了</p>
<p begin="9479400000t" end="9514500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">你是侦探或个人调查员之类的吧</p>
<p begin="9514500000t" end="9547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">是被我太太的家属委托调查</p>
<p begin="9547000000t" end="9582000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">甚至在我家装了窃听器才知道这些的吧</p>
<p begin="9588300000t" end="9628300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">虽说像你这样的女孩从事这类工作很反常</p>
<p begin="9628300000t" end="9651700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">但你实际上并不如外表般年幼</p>
<p begin="9651700000t" end="9690500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">这样你刚才进鳗鱼专卖店的理由也明朗了</p>
<p begin="9690500000t" end="9713400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">八成是为了将我逼入绝境</p>
<p begin="9713400000t" end="9738400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">先跑来观察情况的吧</p>
<p begin="9738400000t" end="9772200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">像你这样的女孩一个人到道地鳗鱼店用餐</p>
<p begin="9772200000t" end="9785500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">再怎么不情愿也会引人注目</p>
<p begin="9785500000t" end="9816800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">如果冷不防地被你搭话问罪</p>
<p begin="9816800000t" end="9845600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">我就会自乱阵脚, 使情势对你有利</p>
<p begin="9845600000t" end="9878600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">说这是天启其实也没错呢</p>
<p begin="9878600000t" end="9932400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">你的确是手持智慧宝剑的虚空藏菩萨</p>
<p begin="9945300000t" end="9975300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">很不巧地我跟菩萨并没有关系</p>
<p begin="9975300000t" end="10006600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">今天会进入你们所在的店家纯粹是偶然</p>
<p begin="10015400000t" end="10028300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">什么嘛…</p>
<p begin="10036600000t" end="10047500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">只不过</p>
<p begin="10047500000t" end="10069200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">我在那边吃鳗鱼饭时</p>
<p begin="10069200000t" end="10087900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">被你太太请托了呢</p>
<p begin="10104200000t" end="10115500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">我妻子?</p>
<p begin="10126300000t" end="10138400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">梶尾先生</p>
<p begin="10138400000t" end="10154700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">你从太太过世后</p>
<p begin="10154700000t" end="10172600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">就一直感到身体沉重</p>
<p begin="10172600000t" end="10196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">每天晚上都睡不着觉对吧</p>
<p begin="10200500000t" end="10214300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">那是当然的</p>
<p begin="10214300000t" end="10247700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">因为被你杀死的太太的亡灵</p>
<p begin="10247700000t" end="10284400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">正牢牢地攀附在你身上</p>
<p begin="10284400000t" end="10297700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">亡灵?</p>
<p begin="10297700000t" end="10347400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">你应该听说过鬼压床或灵障之类的现象吧</p>
<p begin="10347400000t" end="10372000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">那就是发生在你身上的现象</p>
<p begin="10372000000t" end="10393190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">你现在感受到的身体异常</p>
<p begin="10393190000t" end="10424500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">并非罪恶感导致的精神压力</p>
<p begin="10431190000t" end="10458290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">而是外在强压在你身上的负荷</p>
<p begin="10470000000t" end="10488300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">我一走进那间鳗鱼专卖店</p>
<p begin="10488300000t" end="10520000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">就看到有个人被充满复仇意志的亡灵缠身</p>
<p begin="10520000000t" end="10535500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">让我稍微吓了一跳呢</p>
<p begin="10542100000t" end="10579700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">你太太的亡灵还主动靠过来</p>
<p begin="10579700000t" end="10604700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">讲出整件事的来龙去脉</p>
<p begin="10604700000t" end="10619700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">被你谋杀之后</p>
<p begin="10619700000t" end="10643100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">你太太就片刻不离地缠着你</p>
<p begin="10643100000t" end="10676400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">所以对你的杀人手法到最近的动向</p>
<p begin="10676400000t" end="10690600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">全都一清二楚</p>
<p begin="10690600000t" end="10711900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">而且就算你自首</p>
<p begin="10711900000t" end="10733200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">你太太似乎也不打算放过你喔</p>
<p begin="10739400000t" end="10756500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">所以说梶尾先生</p>
<p begin="10756500000t" end="10783600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">就算你自首做了社会性的赎罪</p>
<p begin="10783600000t" end="10802400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">症状也不会改善</p>
<p begin="10802400000t" end="10825800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">建议你今后还是继续这样生活下去吧</p>
<p begin="10867900000t" end="10909200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">拜托你不要胡扯什么亡灵啊鬼压床之类的</p>
<p begin="10909200000t" end="10935900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">我从决定自首后身体就变轻松很多</p>
<p begin="10935900000t" end="10955100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">晚上也能入睡了</p>
<p begin="10955100000t" end="10979300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">这都是我的罪恶感减轻带来的效果</p>
<p begin="10979300000t" end="11003000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">那只是你的错觉</p>
<p begin="11003000000t" end="11018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">是因为你一心认为设法赎罪</p>
<p begin="11018000000t" end="11042600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">症状就会消失</p>
<p begin="11042600000t" end="11061800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">所以才感觉好像好转了</p>
<p begin="11073100000t" end="11110600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">你看, 你现在身体是不是很沉重啊</p>
<p begin="11263300000t" end="11290400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">你太太拜托我传话给你</p>
<p begin="11296700000t" end="11340400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">你不是个会因罪恶感搞垮身体的正常人</p>
<p begin="11346300000t" end="11398400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">出于过强的独占欲而谋杀妻子还不思反省</p>
<p begin="11398400000t" end="11415900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">根本不能称之为人</p>
<p begin="11424700000t" end="11442200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">你太太似乎对于</p>
<p begin="11442200000t" end="11484300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">你认为自己是个有罪恶感的正常人</p>
<p begin="11484300000t" end="11505600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">感到非常火大</p>
<p begin="11505600000t" end="11528100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">而你所谓的罪恶感</p>
<p begin="11528100000t" end="11565700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">只不过是用来说服自己身体不适有其原因</p>
<p begin="11565700000t" end="11588600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">捏造出来的谎言</p>
<p begin="11588600000t" end="11609500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">完全是你的错觉</p>
<p begin="11615300000t" end="11657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">无论你要自首还是继续照常生活都无所谓</p>
<p begin="11657400000t" end="11677900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">吃牢饭虽然不自由</p>
<p begin="11677900000t" end="11697500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">但衣食住是有保障的</p>
<p begin="11697500000t" end="11714600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">照常生活虽然自由</p>
<p begin="11714600000t" end="11755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">- 怎么会, 竟然有这种事</p>
<p begin="11765900000t" end="11784600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">不晓得哪边比较轻松呢</p>
<p begin="11817200000t" end="11831400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">等等</p>
<p begin="11831400000t" end="11850100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">你能看见幽灵</p>
<p begin="11850100000t" end="11865500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">也能听见幽灵的声音对吧</p>
<p begin="11865500000t" end="11898500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">那你应该也能祛除附在我身上的妻子吧</p>
<p begin="11898500000t" end="11909300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">拜托了</p>
<p begin="11909300000t" end="11934000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">能请你救救我吗, 我愿意支付代价</p>
<p begin="11944000000t" end="11967700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">我是妖怪, 精怪</p>
<p begin="11967700000t" end="11996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">幽灵, 魔物等存在的智慧之神</p>
<p begin="11996100000t" end="12025700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">就算接受你身为亡灵的太太的请求</p>
<p begin="12025700000t" end="12049100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">也没有义务接受人类的委托</p>
<p begin="12054900000t" end="12079900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">要是你被太太亡灵纠缠一事</p>
<p begin="12079900000t" end="12107500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">有违人世常理的话, 倒还有余地</p>
<p begin="12107500000t" end="12143700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">但你这是因果报应, 非常合乎道理</p>
<p begin="12143700000t" end="12166700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">无须我出手干涉</p>
<p begin="12166700000t" end="12203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">反正你太太迟早也会对纠缠你感到厌烦</p>
<p begin="12209200000t" end="12234700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">你只要好好活到那时就行了</p>
<p begin="12234700000t" end="12245900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">再说</p>
<p begin="12245900000t" end="12279300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">你现在可是跟爱到杀了她的太太绑在一起</p>
<p begin="12279300000t" end="12294700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">这不正是你的愿望吗</p>
<p begin="12300100000t" end="12320600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">这女孩到底是什么鬼东西</p>
<p begin="12326400000t" end="12359000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">只要像对付雪枝那样抓住头去撞墙…</p>
<p begin="12370200000t" end="12407300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">这种小丫头根本就…</p>
<p begin="12433600000t" end="12446600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">菩萨…</p>
<p begin="12446600000t" end="12463600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">就说你认错人了</p>
<p begin="12468200000t" end="12504100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">至少最后回答我这个问题吧</p>
<p begin="12504100000t" end="12542100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">你刚才为什么会独自进入那家鳗鱼专卖店</p>
<p begin="12542100000t" end="12570400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">我一直在意得不得了…</p>
<p begin="12570400000t" end="12583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">问我为什么</p>
<p begin="12588800000t" end="12611700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">因为我今晚要去男友家过夜</p>
<p begin="12611700000t" end="12636300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">突然想要吃点能增强精力的东西</p>
<p begin="12642600000t" end="12667600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">刚好看到那间鳗鱼专卖店就走进去了</p>
<p begin="12687200000t" end="12721000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">鳗鱼被称为孩子及安产的象征</p>
<p begin="12721000000t" end="12744300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">由于外型和男性生殖器很像</p>
<p begin="12744300000t" end="12767300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">也被视为夫妇和睦的象征呢</p>
<p begin="12773100000t" end="12796500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">深闺千金居然…</p>
<p begin="12796500000t" end="12820200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">感觉吃了就能精力百倍呢</p>
<p begin="12820200000t" end="12841100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">菩萨的化身竟然…</p>
<p begin="12846100000t" end="12861500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">今晚的我可是干劲十足</p>
<p begin="12866100000t" end="12891200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">讲出如此猥亵的话…</p>
<p begin="12891200000t" end="12912400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">那么, 祝你有个美好的余生</p>
<p begin="12959100000t" end="12975800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">夫妇和睦…</p>
<p begin="12995000000t" end="13007100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">雪枝…</p>
<p begin="13039600000t" end="13070100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">原来我称不上是人啊…</p>
<p begin="13081800000t" end="13104700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">九郎同学, 辛苦了</p>
<p begin="13104700000t" end="13116400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">您辛苦了</p>
<p begin="13121800000t" end="13140200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">来接你的人也到了</p>
<p begin="13140200000t" end="13159300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">那个放好你就下班吧</p>
<p begin="13159300000t" end="13172300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">有人来接我?</p>
<p begin="13172300000t" end="13182300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">学长</p>
<p begin="13213600000t" end="13225200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">辛苦了</p>
<p begin="13236900000t" end="13259000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">发生了这样的事呢</p>
<p begin="13259000000t" end="13295300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">那个叫梶尾的人虽然是自作自受</p>
<p begin="13295300000t" end="13323300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">不过你也真不留情呢</p>
<p begin="13323300000t" end="13365800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">我只是尽身为怪物们智慧之神的义务罢了</p>
<p begin="13365800000t" end="13390000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">那个事到如今就不提了</p>
<p begin="13390000000t" end="13430000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">但你以后别再一个人跑去那种鳗鱼店了</p>
<p begin="13438800000t" end="13473000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">店里的人肯定都觉得这个客人很怪</p>
<p begin="13473000000t" end="13499700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">我自己是觉得没什么问题啦</p>
<p begin="13508400000t" end="13543900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">还是说该去吃鳖料理才对呢</p>
<p begin="13543900000t" end="13567700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">就各种意味来说都拜托你别去</p>
<p begin="13567700000t" end="13580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">我是说真的</p>
<p begin="13588900000t" end="13625600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">你是忌妒我一个人跑去吃高级鳗鱼饭吗</p>
<p begin="13630200000t" end="13659800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">但学长你从中午就要打工</p>
<p begin="13659800000t" end="13682000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">就算我邀你也不能来吧</p>
<p begin="13697800000t" end="13733700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">不然下次我再找个机会请你吃?</p>
